headline: The Williams Companies, Inc. (WMB) Plots $3.1B Investment to Bolster Power Generation
summary: The Williams Companies, Inc. (NYSE:WMB) is one of the most profitable energy stocks to buy right now. On October 1, the company announced plans to invest $3.1 billion to enhance its power generation capacity. The transaction is expected to close in the first half of 2027.
